# sunset.scene - warm low light raking across spheres and boxes.
# A single low, warm key light casts long soft-edged shadows over a matte
# floor, with a graded orange-to-purple sky behind.

camera  0 0.8 0  0.5

sky  0.95 0.55 0.25   0.35 0.20 0.45

# Low warm sun from the left, plus a faint cool bounce.
light  -9  1.5 1.0   1.0 0.7 0.4   2.0
light   5  3.0 -2.0  0.4 0.5 0.8   0.4

plane  0 1 0  1.0   0.20 0.18 0.22   0.30 0.27 0.32

sphere -1.6 0.4 4.5  0.6   0.80 0.30 0.10
sphere  0.2 0.6 5.2  0.8   0.95 0.85 0.70   reflect 0.3 140
sphere  1.9 0.3 4.2  0.5   0.40 0.20 0.55

box  -0.9 -1.0 5.8   0.1 0.2 6.6    0.25 0.45 0.75
box   1.1 -1.0 5.5   1.9 0.5 6.3    0.85 0.70 0.20
